  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to examine the correlation between the severity of non-alcoholic
      steatohepatitis/non alcoholic fatty liver disease (NASH/NAFLD) in na√Øve and hepatitis C (HCV)
      positive patients and the amplitude of alpha-defensin immunohistochemical staining in liver
      biopsy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
